data.description: Spacious and captivating 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home with sought after walkout basement nestled on a large, well-manicured lot, centrally located in the heart of Branson, right off Fall Creek Rd, easily accessible to shopping, entertainment, and Table Rock Lake!! Sprawling, open floor layout coupled with beautiful hardwood floors provide a bright welcome! Chic kitchen boasts granite countertops, custom-built cabinets, large gourmet island and plenty of storage!! NEW roof, big bedrooms, large private, master ensuite, jetted tub, huge, covered deck with tree-lined views, and oversized 2 garage make this alluring property a must-see!! Bonus feature: a separate, private driveway to the lower level could be utilized as the perfect mother-in-law quarters or apartment!! Vast, move-in ready, and convenient location make this home absolutely desirable!! Call today!
